        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks CD for his kindness and hopes one day to return it.</p>
            <p>Finds more and more observations fall in with CD’s theory but still finds it difficult to account for the sudden leaps in the fossil record and to explain why some organisms first appear as such high forms.</p>
        </abstract>
